  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in the Atal Pension Yojana (APY). To do so, you typically need to submit a request to your bank or the financial institution where you opened your APY account. Here are the general steps you may follow:\n\n1. **Visit Your Bank**: Go to the branch of the bank where your APY account is held.\n\n2. **Obtain the Form**: Request a nominee change form or any specific form they require for this process.\n\n3. **Fill Out the Form**: Provide the necessary details for the new nominee, such as the nominee\u2019s name, relationship with you, and any required identification details.\n\n4. **Submit the Form**: Return the completed form to the bank, along with any required identification proof or other documents if necessary.\n\n5. **Confirmation**: After your request is processed, you should receive a confirmation from the bank regarding the change of nominee.\n\nIt's advisable to check directly with your bank for any specific procedures or requirements they may have.",
